|-
| Cajal bodies || 0.2–2.0&amp;nbsp;µm || &lt;ref name=&quot;Cioce&quot;&gt;{{cite  journal  | author = Cioce M, Lamond A | title = Cajal bodies: a long history of discovery | journal = Annu Rev Cell Dev Biol | volume = 21 | issue = | pages = 105–131 | year = 2005| pmid = 16212489 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.cellbio.20.010403.103738  }}&lt;/ref&gt;
|-
| PIKA || 5&amp;nbsp;µm || &lt;ref name=&quot;Pollard&quot;&gt;{{cite book
