      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Dablink|&quot;Christmas Day&quot; redirects here. For other uses, see [[Christmas (disambiguation)]] and [[Christmas Day (disambiguation)]].}}
{{pp-semi|small=yes}}{{pp-move-indef}}
